#profile-wrapper.hide
  .profile-settings
    .heading
      .circle
        i.icon-user
      h1= t('settings.profile')
    form.form(action="/settings/profile", method="post", role="form", autocomplete="off", autovalidate='autovalidate', autosubmit='autosubmit')
      
      ul.form-messages
      .form-group
        label #{t('settings.first-name')}
        input.form-control(type='text', id="firstName", name='firstName', tabindex=1, placeholder=t('settings.first-name'), value='#{citizen.firstName}', validate='required firstname')
      .form-group
        label #{t('settings.last-name')}
        input.form-control(type='text', id="lastName", name='lastName', tabindex=2, placeholder=t('settings.last-name'), value='#{citizen.lastName}', validate='required lastname')
      .form-group
        label= t('signup.email')
        input.form-control(type='text', disabled='disabled' name='email', tabindex=3, placeholder=t('forgot.mail.example'), value='#{citizen.email}', validate='required email')
      .form-group.panel.panel-default
        label.panel-heading CEP
        .ask-cep.alert.alert-warning.panel-body
          |<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>  <strong>Pra que pedimos o CEP</strong>
          p
          p
            |Você não é obrigado a preencher esse campo, mas fornecendo essa informação conseguiremos criar gráficos e mapas da sua cidade com as diferentes concentrações de votos por região.
        input.form-control(type='text', id="cep", name='cep', tabindex=3, placeholder='CEP', value='#{citizen.cep}')
      .form-group.profile-picture
        .image-container
          img(src=citizen.profilePicture(), width="65")
        .controls
          a(href="https://gravatar.com", target="_blank")
            strong= t('settings.change-at-gravatar')
          input.form-control(type='text', name='profilePictureUrl', tabindex=4, placeholder=t('settings.paste-url-image'), value=citizen.profilePictureUrl, validate='url')
      .form-group: button.btn.btn-success.btn-block.btn-lg(tabindex=5)=t('settings.save')
